    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, offering a reliable driving experience for its next owner. The exterior is clean and presents well, though you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and small surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is tidy and odor-free, with only light wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it runs smoothly, and all major systems are functioning as they should, making this a solid choice for anyone seeking a dependable car without the new-car price tag.",
